				<description>&lt;p&gt;Will Bergstrom is Anne-Marit&amp;rsquo;s grandson and a gifted writer who collaborated with her on two children&amp;rsquo;s books — &lt;em&gt;The Magic Telescope&lt;/em&gt; (2007) and &lt;em&gt;People of the Prairie&lt;/em&gt; (2008), both illustrated by Anne-Marit. His storytelling and her paintings made for a natural partnership across two generations.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;in-the-news&#34;&gt;In the News&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-harvard-crimson--february-23-2012&#34;&gt;The Harvard Crimson — February 23, 2012&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://annemaritbergstrom.com/images/publications/it_takes_two.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Harvard Crimson — It Takes Two&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://annemaritbergstrom.com/images/publications/it_takes_two-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Harvard Crimson — It Takes Two (continued)&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;fargo-forum--december-2008&#34;&gt;Fargo Forum — December 2008&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://annemaritbergstrom.com/images/publications/fargo_forum-12-08.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Fargo Forum — People of the Prairie&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
